Title: Relates to brand-name drugs with and without an AB generic equivalent
Summary: Relates to brand-name drugs with and without an AB generic equivalent; amends the effective date from January to July next succeeding the date on which it shall have become a law.
LawCode: Amd §§3216, 3221 & 4303, Ins L; amd §4, Chap of 2022 (as proposed in S.5299-A & A.1741-A)
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the insurance law, in relation to calculating an insured individual's overall contribution to any out-of-pocket maximum or any cost-sharing requirement; and to amend a chapter of the laws of 2022 amending the insurance law relating to calculating an insured individual's overall contribution to any out-of-pocket maximum or any cost-sharing requirement, as proposed in legislative bills numbers S. 5299-A and A. 1741-A, in relation to the effectiveness thereof
